title: BRIEF-Intel Announces Judgment For Remaining Mobileye Shares Acquisition
text:
March 29, 2018 / 1:06 PM / Updated 11 minutes ago BRIEF-Intel Announces Judgment For Remaining Mobileye Shares Acquisition Reuters Staff 
  Intel Corp: 
* INTEL ANNOUNCES JUDGMENT OF THE ENTERPRISE CHAMBER IN COMPULSORY ACQUISITION PROCEEDING FOR REMAINING MOBILEYE SHARES 
* INTEL - ENTERPRISE CHAMBER ORDERED ALL MINORITY MOBILEYE SHAREHOLDERS TO TRANSFER THEIR SHARES TO CYCLOPS IN EXCHANGE FOR PAYMENT OF $63.54/SHARE IN CASH 
* INTEL - FROM MARCH 27 TO APRIL 25, MOBILEYE SHAREHOLDERS CAN ADHERE TO THE ENTERPRISE CHAMBER JUDGMENT BY TRANSFERRING THEIR MOBILEYE SHARES TO CYCLOPS HOLDINGS Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
